processIncomingData() - Static method in class node.threads.DataRetrieverThread
This processes data sent by the server after either a DATA_DIFF_REQUEST or an ALL_DATA_REQUEST.
Protocol is:
read some_DATA_REQUEST
while(response!=END_OF_DATA)
if (CLEAR_MEMORY_REQUEST)
clear memory
else (MALICIOUS_IP_ADDITION || MALICIOUS_STRING_ADDITION || MALICIOUS_IP_REMOVAL || MALICIOUS_STRING_REMOVAL)
read data length
read data and add them to memory
else
error
